#: upstream/_versions/1.7/guides/deploying-to-openshift.adoc:163
#, no-wrap
msgid "Environment variables from Secret"
msgstr "シークレットからの環境変数"

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_versions/1.7/guides/deploying-to-openshift.adoc:166
